platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A well is usually one of the last things we’d want to fall into, but this retro-style shooter has us jumping in again and again. It’s a rush descending from rock to rock, blasting creepy creatures with your gunboots while nabbing crimson gems. Roguelike difficulty means you’re in for a challenge, but superb controls and nifty upgrades (including a jetpack, a drone, and laser sights) give you all the help you’ll need. And with randomly generated levels, each journey feels as fresh and exciting as the last.

A well is usually one of the last things we’d want to fall into, but this retro-style shooter has us jumping in again and again. It’s a rush descending from rock to rock, blasting creepy creatures with your gunboots while nabbing crimson gems. Roguelike difficulty means you’re in for a challenge, but superb controls and nifty upgrades (including a jetpack, a drone and laser sights) give you all the help you’ll need. And with randomly generated levels, each journey feels as fresh and exciting as the last.

Sautez à pieds joints dans un puits et laissez-vous entraîner dans un jeu de tir à l’ambiance rétro. Dirigez-vous vers les profondeurs tout en anéantissant les créatures malfaisantes et en collectant les pierres précieuses sur votre chemin. La difficulté particulièrement élevée mettra à l’épreuve vos talents de gamer, alors que les commandes d’une grande précision et les différents upgrades (jetpack, visée laser ou encore drone) vous seront indispensables au fil des niveaux générés aléatoirement.
